very 30 minutes or so, if even that often. Result was, two frustrated people, five hours lost, no hearts, /ooc'd to no end. The day ended with my friend falling in the lava and in an interesting CR.<br><br>So, here's where I am. My wizard has the Staff of ro, my shaman the heart of frost and rod of bone. If I can get the heart of fire for my shaman, can I hand them to Gardern, and then get wizard to hand him the staff of ro? They are both on the same account.<br><br>If I ever get out of there, I will never ever step a foot in SolA again.<br><br>-Rotbone Binkbonk, 56th level Oger shaman<br>-Cendywen, 28th level high elf wizard<br>Innoruuk <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utaarne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taarne</A> at: 9/28/02 1:43:12 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utehutibloodstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tehuti Bloodstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Blueberry Nuker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/28/02 5:33:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=604.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: MQing SoTF?</span><hr size=1> Yes. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uhibashira.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hibashira</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/28/02 12:46:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=604.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   