gn=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ayep</span><hr size=1> Not that you need any more confirmation.  But... Yep, I did the SoTF quest for my baby wizard that way.  Just make sure both of your faction is ok.  I usually run thru the quest dialog with both char.  <br><br>My main turned in the stuff, camped, brought on my baby wiz and she turned in her darkwood staff thing and ... presto!<br><br>Sol A is like that btw.  My first time doing this quest, I got lucky and some ppl (60 monk, cleric and wiz) were clearing the zone to encourage lord Gimblox (clr epic) to spawn.  Took about 20 min to get the heart.  My second time (for my baby wiz) it took fore.v..e...r  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=604.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=604.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=604.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=604.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.threadControl?topicID=604.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=604.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a hr